User
    ident       Text
    password    Text Maybe
    UniqueUser  ident
    deriving Typeable

Users
    name        Text
    password    Text
    email       Text
    friends     Int List
    reviews     Text Maybe List
    movies      Movie Maybe List

Email
    email       Text
    user        UserId Maybe
    verkey      Text Maybe
    UniqueEmail email


Movie
    title       Text
    picture     Text
    genre       Text
    rating      Text
    synopsis    Text
    userReviews Text
    year        Text
    director    Text

Review
    content     Text
    movieId     Movie
    userId      User


